app_name: Groups Treatment Groups Apple Translate Wisdom Elf Quick Translation
app_description: Wisdom Elf Quick Translation is an accurate and fast handheld translation application that brings you a fast accurate and convenient translation experience. Whether it s business communication international travel or cultural exchange this app can become your most effective language assistant. Wisdom Elf Quick Translation with advanced translation technology and intelligent algorithms can instantly convert multiple major languages into each other. Simply enter or say what needs to be translated and Wisdom Elf Quick Translation will immediately provide you with high quality translation results. Not only that Wisdom Elf Quick Translation also provides real time photography and voice translation functions allowing you to directly upload the content you need to translate through images and voice. The simple and intuitive interface design of Wisdom Elf Quick Translation also provides convenience for your operation.
